on Gano|url=http://www.violentfemmes.net/gordon.htm|accessdate=2007-08-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703103351/http://www.violentfemmes.net/gordon.htm|archivedate=July 3, 2007}}</ref> *[[1964]] &ndash; [[Gia Carides]], Australian actress * 1964 &ndash; [[Graeme Labrooy]], Sri Lankan cricketer *[[1965]] &ndash; [[Mick Foley]], American wrestler, actor, and author * 1965 &ndash; [[Jean-Pierre François]], French footballer and singer * 1965 &ndash; [[Damien Hirst]], English painter and art collector *[[1966]] &ndash; [[Eric Kretz]], American drummer, songwriter, and producer * 1966 &ndash; [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]], American director, screenwriter and actor * 1966 &ndash; [[Stéphane Richer (ice hockey forward)|Stéphane Richer]], Canadian ice hockey player *[[1967]] &ndash; [[Dave Navarro]], American singer-songwriter, guitarist, and producer *[[1970]] &ndash; [[Helen Baxendale]], English actress * 1970 &ndash; [[Cafu]], Brazilian footballer * 1970 &ndash; [[Andrei Kovalenko]], Russian ice hockey player * 1970 &ndash; [[Mike Modano]], American ice hockey player *[[1972]] &ndash; [[Karl Urban]], New Zealand actor *[[1974]] &ndash; [[Bear Grylls]], English adventurer, author, and television host *[[1975]] &ndash; [[Allen Iverson]], American basketball player *[[1976]] &ndash; [[Necro (rapper)|Necro]], American rapper, producer, and director * 1976 &ndash; [[Mirsad Türkcan]], Turkish basketball player *[[1977]] &ndash; [[Marcin Baszczyński]], Polish footballer *[[1978]] &ndash; [[Mini Andén]], Swedish-American model, actress, and producer * 1978 &ndash; [[Bill Hader]], American actor, comedian, and screenwriter *[[1979]] &ndash; [[Kevin Hofland]], Dutch footballer * 1979 &ndash; [[Anna Torv]], Australian actress *[[1980]] &ndash; [[Ed Moses (swimmer)|Ed Moses]], American swimmer *[[1981]] &ndash; [[Stephen Bywater]], English footballer * 1981 &ndash; [[Anna Kournikova]], Russian tennis player * 1981 &ndash; [[Kevin Kyle]], Scottish footballe